If you are like me and looking for a way to prepare the perfect hassle-free tea, check out my recently discovered kickass TEA MAKER by @thetdtworld ✨⁣
⁣
It is so simple to use and maintain, and the best part is, that I can choose how strong I want my tea, which is honestly a lifesaver 🙌

PS: Mother's Day is just around the corner. If your mum is a tea lover, this would be a perfect delight for her ☕🎁

In 2013, I had the good fortune of visiting Faro & Lisbon in Portugal and was right away taken by the beautiful tiles that are the roots of Portuguese culture cemented around the city! From the beautiful beaches to the history of Portugal many years later is still etched in my mind like it was yesterday ✈️

Watch the video to experience Portugal 🇵🇹 at @expo2020dubai 

With an assortment of digital experiences about Portuguese culture and heritage, beautiful music, reflecting great innovation and prospects virtually. 

A quick fact about the country: Portugal is the third most peaceful country in the world according to the Global Peace Index 2019.

I am a big fan of anything and everything personalised. 
Recently, I came across this page on Instagram that customises gadgets, and I was intrigued to get something personalised that I love. 

After months of brainstorming with @foxmybox team and understanding the different ways to personalise the gadgets, I'm so excited to use my personalised Dyson Supersonic. 

Gold leafing initial and the stunning dark metallic violet colour overall just look so stunning and I LOVE IT ✨💜💫

 Do check them out if you would like to get your gadgets personalised. 

PS: They got my Dyson picked up from home and delivered safely. My biggest concern was that the product should not get lost or damaged in transit, but they managed to do everything so flawlessly.

✨ Things to Know Before You Go to Egypt! ✨
Planning your Egyptian adventure? Here’s your cheat sheet:
🛂 E-visa? Apply early.
🗣️ Arabic? Gorgeous—just keep a translator handy.
🧥 Evenings? Cooler than you think. Bring layers.
💃 Nile Cruise? Yes, pack those party shoes.
🕌 Fridays? Like Sundays—expect slower hours during prayers.

Travel smart, explore smoother!
